# Cursor rules bridge

Read `AGENTS.md` first. This file intentionally stays short so Cursor-specific rules do not drift away from the shared AI Agent instructions.

- Follow root `AGENTS.md` and the nearest nested `AGENTS.md`.
- Keep generated edits consistent with Vue 3 + NestJS + pnpm workspace boundaries documented in `docs/`.
- Do not duplicate long project rules here. Update `AGENTS.md` or `docs/agents/*` instead.
- Treat commands in this example as target-project examples, not commands for the current skill repository.

